        <mxCell id="p1-firewall" value="&lt;b&gt;aws_networkfirewall_firewall.main&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;AWS Network Firewall  ← new&#xa;─────────────────&#xa;• Dedicated /28 subnets (×3 AZ)&#xa;• Stateful inspection (STRICT_ORDER)&#xa;• Policy: block_threats rule group&#xa;• North-south + east-west&#xa;• Delete protection: enabled&#xa;• Subnet change protection: on&#xa;• Flow log + Alert log → CW" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#b6d7a8;strokeColor=#38761d;align=left;spacingLeft=8;fontSize=10;strokeWidth=2;" vertex="1" parent="1">
